Pam Dawber https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pam_Dawber 0 Pamela Dawber (born October 18, 1951) is an American actress best known for her lead television sitcom roles as Mindy McConnell in Mork Mindy (1978–1982) and Samantha Russell in My Sister Sam (1986–1988).
